dataset.name: Zillow Home Value Index (Zip): Median Rental Price - Studio - 10013, New York, NY
dataset.description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of median rental price - studio within the zip of 10013, New York, NY. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
